extendedInfo.description: *Full version out now*Box Fox is a 2D platformer with a heavy focus on puzzles, it takes inspiration from classics such as Incredible Machine, Sokoban and Block Dude, as well as modern games such as Portal and Minecraft.Features:-Lots of puzzle elements including buttons, doors, movable bridges, springs, teleporters, pushers, keys, etc-Challenging puzzles that aim to make you think, as well as easy levels for casual gamers.-All levels can be skipped. -Fullscreen support for honeycomb tablet devices.Email me, or post on the forums if you have any problems or requests for the game.
